    "This could constrain content moderation efforts just when AI's speed and scale would be most useful.",
    "Policymakers thus face a difficult task in reconciling robust privacy protections with agile anti-disinformation mechanisms.",
    "In addition, there are practical and resource challenges.",
    "Disinformation is a cross-border, cross-platform problem, but enforcement mechanisms are typically national.",
    "Even when countries agree on principles, coordinating actions (such as shutting down a global botnet or sanctioning a foreign propaganda outlet) is cumbersome."
